Package: LanguageToolR
Title: Provides a wrapper for the LanguageTool CLI tool for spelling, grammar and language checking
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Clemens", "Schmid", email = "clemens@nevrome.de", role = c("cre", "cph", "aut")),
